    "body": "OK, I tried to reproduce this bug on Google Chrome Version 57.0.2987.98 (64-bit) on macOS 10.12.3 (starting it in command line with `LANG=fr_FR.UTF-8` set), and it happens to make Google Chrome totally unusable on most websites. Here is an screenshot on MDN:\r\n![capture d ecran 2017-03-28 a 11 37 44](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/7548264/24398937/7106c48a-13ab-11e7-96ba-e7a8f1ae77e9.png)\r\n\r\nI didn't investigate further."
